P-P-029.name: Bartolomeo
P-P-029.Description: [End of Your Turn] You may rest this Character: Set up to 1 of your "FILM" type Characters other than [Bartolomeo] as active.

P-P-057.name: Fleeting Lullaby
P-P-057.Description:
[Main] If your Leader is [Uta], up to 2 of your opponent's rested Characters with a cost of 4 or less will not become active in your opponent's next Refresh Phase.

[Trigger] Activate this card's [Main] effect.

P-P-058.name: Where the Wind Blows
P-P-058.Description:
[Main] If your Leader is [Uta], set all of your "FILM" type Characters as active at the end of this turn.

[Trigger] Set all of your "FILM" type Characters as active.

P-P-059.name: The World's Continuation
P-P-059.Description: [Counter] If your Leader is [Uta], you may return any number of Characters on your field to the owner's hand. Up to 1 of your Leader or Character cards gains +2000 power during this battle for every returned Character.

P-P-060.name: Tot Musica
P-P-060.Description: [Main] You may rest 1 of your [Uta] cards: Rest up to 2 of your opponent's DON!! cards.

ST11-ST11-001 foil.name: Uta (ST11-001)
ST11-ST11-001 foil.Description: [DON!! x1] [When Attacking] [Once Per Turn] Reveal 1 card from the top of your deck and add up to 1 "FILM" type card to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck.

ST11-ST11-003.name: Backlight
ST11-ST11-003.Description:
[Main] If your Leader is [Uta], choose one:

• Rest up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a cost of 5 or less.

• K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's rested Characters with a cost of 5 or less.

ST11-ST11-004.name: New Genesis
ST11-ST11-004.Description: [Main] If your Leader is [Uta], look at 3 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 1 "FILM" type card other than [New Genesis] and add it to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order and set up to 1 of your DON!! cards as active.

ST11-ST11-005.name: I'm invincible
ST11-ST11-005.Description:
[Main] Set up to 1 of your [Uta] Leader as active.

[Trigger] Up to 1 of your Leader or Character cards gains +1000 power during this turn.

ST16-ST16-001 foil.name: Uta (ST16-001)
ST16-ST16-001 foil.Description:
[Blocker] (After your opponent declares an attack, you may rest this card to make it the new target of the attack.)

[Activate: Main] [Once Per Turn] You may trash 1 "FILM" type card from your hand: Give up to 1 rested DON!! card to your Leader or 1 of your Characters.

ST16-ST16-002.name: Gordon
ST16-ST16-002.Description:
[Blocker] (After your opponent declares an attack, you may rest this card to make it the new target of the attack.)

[On Your Opponent's Attack] You may trash any number of "Music" type cards from your hand. Your Leader or 1 of your Characters gains +1000 power during this battle for every card trashed.

ST16-ST16-003.name: Charlotte Katakuri
ST16-ST16-003.Description: If your Leader has the "FILM" type and you have 6 or more rested cards, this Character gains +2000 power.

ST16-ST16-004 foil.name: Shanks
ST16-ST16-004 foil.Description: [On Play] K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's rested Characters.

ST16-ST16-005.name: Monkey.D.Luffy (ST16-005)
ST16-ST16-005.Description: If you have a rested [Uta], this Character gains +1000 power.
